{
  "stem": "19923.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 254.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it was totally black.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was so starved that I ate that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I remember eating it and feeling satisfied.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But we--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Frank, Alex Frank.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was only 28 years old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was the head of the group.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a communist, a Belgian communist.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he was in charge of the boys' home and he survived the war and he's still alive today in Germany.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he took charge of the group and he probably was the oldest adult.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The-- some of the people in-- in our group were teenagers or already-- 13, 14, 15, 16-year-olds.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And of course, they helped out and of course, there were some as young as three years old.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that the age group of all the children varied and the older ones took on more responsibility in keeping the group together.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- they would go and work in the fields for farmers for-- in exchange for food.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They would find any work that was available where they could get some benefits from that to help us survive.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You were saying in the granary at that point?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That granary we turned into a home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After the beds came and the blankets came, then the whole place was changed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- one of the rooms we use for a dining room, another one we used for-- a big hall, we used for a bedroom.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, when we talk about the cots, the cots were put right next to each other so there was no room in between.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in order to get everybody to sleep, you would-- some people would have to sleep between the cots and it became kind of difficult sometimes to start sleeping there.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
